Beat him up! Beat him up!

84
00:13:09,789 --> 00:13:14,749
What! Dead already?

85
00:13:17,797 --> 00:13:19,765
He's not Magic Shot Bandit.

86
00:13:19,799 --> 00:13:21,767
The gun's fake too.

87
00:13:21,801 --> 00:13:26,761
You have guts!

88
00:13:35,815 --> 00:13:40,775


