You traded me for a mule! Go live with your mule.

131
00:25:25,524 --> 00:25:30,484
I'm going, and I'm never coming back!

132
00:25:30,529 --> 00:25:35,489
Disowning your father!  You little bitch! Not so easy!

133
00:25:35,534 --> 00:25:40,494
