135
00:25:45,544 --> 00:25:49,503
Big head-Li was murdered at 18 Mile Slope.

136
00:25:49,548 --> 00:25:53,507
No one knew who killed him.

137
00:25:53,552 --> 00:25:58,512
I always thought grandpa did it.

138
00:25:58,557 --> 00:26:03,517
But I never had a chance to ask him before he died.

139
00:26:05,564 --> 00:26:10,524
We'd better leave, and find work elsewhere.

140
00:26:10,569 --> 00:26:13,538
This leper house is jinxed anyway.

141
00:26:13,572 --> 00:26:16,541
That woman brought nothing but trouble.

142
00:26:16,575 --> 00:26:21,535
It's very strange.

143
00:26:21,580 --> 00:26:26,540
