147
00:26:38,597 --> 00:26:42,556
No one knew what happened at Green Killer's Crossing.

148
00:26:42,601 --> 00:26:47,561
The county sent two investigators...they didn't find anything!

149
00:26:48,607 --> 00:26:53,567
