152
00:27:03,622 --> 00:27:07,581
they only wanted him dead.

153
00:27:07,626 --> 00:27:12,586
That woman...she didn't waste any time!

154
00:27:13,632 --> 00:27:18,592
On the wedding day, she and the sedan bearer were eyeing each other.

155
00:27:21,640 --> 00:27:26,600
What's it to us?  Tomorrow we'll pack and leave.

156
00:27:26,645 --> 00:27:27,612
See no evil, hear no evil.

157
00:27:27,646 --> 00:27:29,614


158
00:27:29,648 --> 00:27:31,616
Come in.

159
00:27:31,650 --> 00:27:33,618
I haven't got my pants on.

160
00:27:33,652 --> 00:27:36,621
Eggy's dad, are you still drinking?

161
00:27:36,655 --> 00:27:38,623
Scolding your husband again?

162
00:27:38,657 --> 00:27:42,616
Go to sleep!

163
00:27:42,661 --> 00:27:46,620
I just saw that woman sitting alone in the courtyard.

164
00:27:46,665 --> 00:27:48,633
It's an eerie sight.

165
00:27:48,667 --> 00:27:51,636
Send her to us! We'll have some fun!

166
00:27:51,670 --> 00:27:56,630
Behave yourself!

167
00:28:26,705 --> 00:28:31,665
She's afraid of the house...afraid to catch leprosy.

168
00:28:52,731 --> 00:28:59,693
Boss!?

169
