Sorghum wine can cure all sickness.

170
00:30:05,804 --> 00:30:07,772
Don't go!

171
00:30:07,806 --> 00:30:12,766
I want to talk to you.  We can't close down the brewery.

172
00:30:12,811 --> 00:30:17,771
Brother Laohan.

173
00:30:17,816 --> 00:30:20,785
Brother Laohan, you were here the longest.

174
00:30:20,819 --> 00:30:25,779
You manage things around here.

175
00:30:25,824 --> 00:30:30,784
I am just a woman, I need your help.

176
00:30:33,832 --> 00:30:38,792
If you really want to go, I won't force you to stay.

177
00:30:39,838 --> 00:30:41,806
You'll get this month's wages, too.

178
00:30:41,840 --> 00:30:46,800
Whenever you want to come back,
you'll have a job waiting.

179
00:30:47,846 --> 00:30:52,806
Please stay.

180
00:30:52,851 --> 00:30:57,811
