187
00:31:13,872 --> 00:31:15,840
We're all equals here.

188
00:31:15,874 --> 00:31:20,834
I am the ninth child, born on the 9th day of the 9th moon.

189
00:31:22,881 --> 00:31:27,841
So, call me Jiu'er (Ninth Child), like everyone else.

190
00:31:29,888 --> 00:31:35,860
Jiu'er.

191
