268
00:42:33,551 --> 00:42:36,520
You dare talk to me like that?!

269
00:42:36,554 --> 00:42:39,523
I won't leave till I get beef.

270
00:42:39,557 --> 00:42:44,517
Sit tight.

271
00:42:45,563 --> 00:42:50,523
